Make sure both the devices on the same network

Laptop (Sender):
You have a file report.pdf in /home/user/Documents.
Start the Python server:

bash
Copy code
cd /home/user/Documents
python3 -m http.server 8000
Other Device (Receiver):
Open the browser and enter:

cpp
Copy code
http://192.168.1.100:8000
Download the report.pdf from the list.

BONUS Tip:
If you need to upload files from the receiver to the sender, you can use uploadserver, a Python package that allows file uploads via the browser. Let me know if you'd like instructions for setting that up!
